# Chrome Extension: Indeed Job Scraper & Auto-Apply

A Chrome extension that scrapes job listings from Indeed and streamlines the job application process. Easily fill out forms and manage job data with persistent browser storage.

## Features

- Scrape job cards and extract details (title, company, location, salary, etc.)
- Auto-fill job application forms
- Modular code structure for easy maintenance
- Persistent storage using Chrome's extension APIs
- Simple messaging between background, popup, and content scripts

## Getting Started

1. Clone this repo.
2. Load the extension in Chrome:
   - Go to `chrome://extensions`
   - Enable "Developer mode"
   - Click "Load unpacked" and select this project folder
3. Open Indeed and click the extension button to start scraping and auto-applying.

## Usage

- Open an Indeed job page.
- Click the extension's "Start" button.
- The extension will scrape job data and help fill out applications.

